                <me>\text{Weighted Average:} \text{Car Quality} = \frac{10R + 5G + 20I + 5C}{40}</me>
                <me>\text{Harris-Benedict for males:} REE = 66.4730 + 13.7516 * W + 5.0033 * H - 6.7550 * A</me>
            </p>
        </introduction>
        <task workspace="0.5in">
